### Role Management API Check File
### Base URL: https://todu.mn/bs/lms/v1
### Supports: List, create, read, update, delete roles (permissions)
### Note: Roles are system-wide. School-level role assignment is handled via school membership requests.

@baseUrl = https://todu.mn/bs/lms/v1
@roleId = 10

### 1. List all roles
# GET /roles
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
# Response: { "items": [ { id, name, priority, created_on, ... } ] }
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2. Create a new role (admin only)
# POST /roles
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
# Request body: name, priority (optional)
POST {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Department Head",
  "priority": 10
}

### 3. Get role by ID
# GET /roles/{role_id}
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Update role (admin only)
# PUT /roles/{role_id}
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
# Request body: name, priority (optional)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Senior Department Head",
  "priority": 15
}

### 5. Delete role (admin only)
# DELETE /roles/{role_id}
# Headers: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}